'''梭菌蛋白酶'''（{{lang-en|Clostripain}}，{{EC number|3.4.22.8}}，其它英文名有：''clostridiopeptidase B'', ''clostridium histolyticum proteinase B'', ''alpha-clostridipain'', ''clostridiopeptidase'', ''Endoproteinase Arg-C''）是一种从[[梭菌属|梭菌属]]{{le|溶组织梭状芽胞杆菌|Clostridium histolyticum}}（''Clostridium histolyticum''）中分离出的[[蛋白酶|蛋白酶]]，在[[精氨酸|精氨酸]]的羧基端水解[[肽键|肽键]]<ref>{{cite journal | title = Cleavage at arginine residues by clostripain |author = Mitchell, W.M. |journal = Methods Enzymol. |year = 1977 |volume = 47 |pages = 165–170 |pmid = 927173 |doi=10.1016/0076-6879(77)47020-4}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = α-Clostripain. Chemical characterization, activity, and thiol content of the highly active form of clostripain |author = Gilles, A.-M., Imhoff, J.-M. and Keil, B. |journal = J. Biol. Chem. |year = 1979 |volume = 254 |pages = 1462–1468 |pmid = 762145}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = Primary structure of α-clostripain light chain |author = Gilles, A.-M., Lecroisey, A. and Keil, B. |journal = Eur. J. Biochem. |year = 1984 |volume = 145 |pages = 469–476 |pmid = 6391922 |doi=10.1111/j.1432-1033.1984.tb08579.x}}</ref>，最适反应pH为7.4~7.8。

